channel.title: Java not in program files
channel.description:
Hey guys i need help!
Please!!
Im trying to put my server online but im trying to change the java in the source/client...there is no java folder in my Program Files..but there is a java folder in my Program Files (x86)...can anyone help me on what i am suppposed to do?

item.title: Java not in program files
item.dc:creator: @vlad1 vlad1
item.description:
@vlad1 wrote:

change the options in the client to programfiles/java/jdk (your jdk) to program files (x86) instead

Hope i helped
